 protected List<Rule> parsePattern(){
 DateFormatSymbols symbols=new DateFormatSymbols(mLocale);
 List<Rule> rules=new ArrayList<Rule>();
 String[] ERAs=symbols.getEras();
 String[] months=symbols.getMonths();
 String[] shortMonths=symbols.getShortMonths();
 String[] weekdays=symbols.getWeekdays();
 String[] shortWeekdays=symbols.getShortWeekdays();
 String[] AmPmStrings=symbols.getAmPmStrings();
 int length=mPattern.length();
 int[] indexRef=new int[1];
 for(int i=0;i<length;i++){
 indexRef[0]=i;
 String token=parseToken(mPattern,indexRef);
 i=indexRef[0];
 int tokenLen=token.length();
 if(tokenLen==0){
 break;
 }
 Rule rule;
 char c=token.charAt(0);
 switch (c){
 case 'G' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.ERA,ERAs);
 break;
 case 'y' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.YEAR,tokenLen);
 }else {
 rule=TwoDigitYearField.INSTANCE;
 }
 break;
 case 'M' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.MONTH,months);
 }else {
 if(tokenLen==3){
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.MONTH,shortMonths);
 }else {
 if(tokenLen==2){
 rule=TwoDigitMonthField.INSTANCE;
 }else {
 rule=UnpaddedMonthField.INSTANCE;
 }
 }
 }
 break;
 case 'd' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'h' :
 
 rule=new TwelveHourField(selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR,tokenLen));
 break;
 case 'H' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR_OF_DAY,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'm' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.MINUTE,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 's' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.SECOND,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'S' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.MILLISECOND,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'E' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.DAY_OF_WEEK,tokenLen<4?shortWeekdays:weekdays);
 break;
 case 'D' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_YEAR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'F' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_WEEK_IN_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'w' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.WEEK_OF_YEAR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'W' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.WEEK_OF_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'a' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.AM_PM,AmPmStrings);
 break;
 case 'k' :
 
 rule=new TwentyFourHourField(selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR_OF_DAY,tokenLen));
 break;
 case 'K' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'z' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=new TimeZoneNameRule(mTimeZone,mTimeZoneForced,mLocale,TimeZone.LONG);
 }else {
 rule=new TimeZoneNameRule(mTimeZone,mTimeZoneForced,mLocale,TimeZone.SHORT);
 }
 break;
 case 'Z' :
 
 if(tokenLen==1){
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_NO_COLON;
 }else {
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_COLON;
 }
 break;
 case '\'' :
 
 String sub=token.substring(1);
 if(sub.length()==1){
 rule=new CharacterLiteral(sub.charAt(0));
 }else {
 rule=new StringLiteral(sub);
+continue;
 }
 break;
 default :
 
 throw new IllegalArgumentException("Illegal pattern component: "+token);
 }
 rules.add(rule);
 }
 return rules;
 }

 protected List<Rule> parsePattern(){
 DateFormatSymbols symbols=new DateFormatSymbols(mLocale);
 List<Rule> rules=new ArrayList<Rule>();
 String[] ERAs=symbols.getEras();
 String[] months=symbols.getMonths();
 String[] shortMonths=symbols.getShortMonths();
 String[] weekdays=symbols.getWeekdays();
 String[] shortWeekdays=symbols.getShortWeekdays();
 String[] AmPmStrings=symbols.getAmPmStrings();
 int length=mPattern.length();
 int[] indexRef=new int[1];
 for(int i=0;i<length;i++){
 indexRef[0]=i;
 String token=parseToken(mPattern,indexRef);
 i=indexRef[0];
 int tokenLen=token.length();
 if(tokenLen==0){
 break;
 }
 Rule rule;
 char c=token.charAt(0);
 switch (c){
 case 'G' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.ERA,ERAs);
 break;
 case 'y' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.YEAR,tokenLen);
 }else {
 rule=TwoDigitYearField.INSTANCE;
 }
 break;
 case 'M' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.MONTH,months);
 }else {
 if(tokenLen==3){
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.MONTH,shortMonths);
 }else {
 if(tokenLen==2){
 rule=TwoDigitMonthField.INSTANCE;
 }else {
 rule=UnpaddedMonthField.INSTANCE;
 }
 }
 }
 break;
 case 'd' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'h' :
 
 rule=new TwelveHourField(selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR,tokenLen));
 break;
 case 'H' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR_OF_DAY,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'm' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.MINUTE,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 's' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.SECOND,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'S' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.MILLISECOND,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'E' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.DAY_OF_WEEK,tokenLen<4?shortWeekdays:weekdays);
 break;
 case 'D' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_YEAR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'F' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_WEEK_IN_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'w' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.WEEK_OF_YEAR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'W' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.WEEK_OF_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'a' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.AM_PM,AmPmStrings);
 break;
 case 'k' :
 
 rule=new TwentyFourHourField(selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR_OF_DAY,tokenLen));
 break;
 case 'K' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'z' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=new TimeZoneNameRule(mTimeZone,mTimeZoneForced,mLocale,TimeZone.LONG);
 }else {
 rule=new TimeZoneNameRule(mTimeZone,mTimeZoneForced,mLocale,TimeZone.SHORT);
 }
 break;
 case 'Z' :
 
 if(tokenLen==1){
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_NO_COLON;
 }else {
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_COLON;
 }
 break;
 case '\'' :
 
 String sub=token.substring(1);
 if(sub.length()==1){
 rule=new CharacterLiteral(sub.charAt(0));
+return null;
 }else {
 rule=new StringLiteral(sub);
 }
 break;
 default :
 
 throw new IllegalArgumentException("Illegal pattern component: "+token);
 }
 rules.add(rule);
 }
 return rules;
 }

 protected List<Rule> parsePattern(){
 DateFormatSymbols symbols=new DateFormatSymbols(mLocale);
 List<Rule> rules=new ArrayList<Rule>();
 String[] ERAs=symbols.getEras();
 String[] months=symbols.getMonths();
 String[] shortMonths=symbols.getShortMonths();
 String[] weekdays=symbols.getWeekdays();
 String[] shortWeekdays=symbols.getShortWeekdays();
 String[] AmPmStrings=symbols.getAmPmStrings();
 int length=mPattern.length();
 int[] indexRef=new int[1];
 for(int i=0;i<length;i++){
 indexRef[0]=i;
 String token=parseToken(mPattern,indexRef);
 i=indexRef[0];
 int tokenLen=token.length();
 if(tokenLen==0){
 break;
 }
 Rule rule;
 char c=token.charAt(0);
 switch (c){
 case 'G' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.ERA,ERAs);
 break;
 case 'y' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.YEAR,tokenLen);
 }else {
 rule=TwoDigitYearField.INSTANCE;
 }
 break;
 case 'M' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.MONTH,months);
 }else {
 if(tokenLen==3){
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.MONTH,shortMonths);
 }else {
 if(tokenLen==2){
 rule=TwoDigitMonthField.INSTANCE;
 }else {
 rule=UnpaddedMonthField.INSTANCE;
 }
 }
 }
 break;
 case 'd' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'h' :
 
 rule=new TwelveHourField(selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR,tokenLen));
 break;
 case 'H' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR_OF_DAY,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'm' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.MINUTE,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 's' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.SECOND,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'S' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.MILLISECOND,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'E' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.DAY_OF_WEEK,tokenLen<4?shortWeekdays:weekdays);
 break;
 case 'D' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_YEAR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'F' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_WEEK_IN_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'w' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.WEEK_OF_YEAR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'W' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.WEEK_OF_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'a' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.AM_PM,AmPmStrings);
 break;
 case 'k' :
 
 rule=new TwentyFourHourField(selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR_OF_DAY,tokenLen));
 break;
 case 'K' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'z' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=new TimeZoneNameRule(mTimeZone,mTimeZoneForced,mLocale,TimeZone.LONG);
 }else {
 rule=new TimeZoneNameRule(mTimeZone,mTimeZoneForced,mLocale,TimeZone.SHORT);
 }
 break;
 case 'Z' :
 
 if(tokenLen==1){
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_NO_COLON;
 }else {
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_COLON;
 }
 break;
 case '\'' :
 
 String sub=token.substring(1);
 if(sub.length()==1){
 rule=new CharacterLiteral(sub.charAt(0));
+init();
 }else {
 rule=new StringLiteral(sub);
 }
 break;
 default :
 
 throw new IllegalArgumentException("Illegal pattern component: "+token);
 }
 rules.add(rule);
 }
 return rules;
 }

 break;

 break;

 break;

 }else {
 rule=new TimeZoneNameRule(mTimeZone,mTimeZoneForced,mLocale,TimeZone.SHORT);
 }
 break;
 case 'Z' :
 
 if(tokenLen==1){
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_NO_COLON;
 }else {
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_COLON;
 }
 break;
 case '\'' :
 
 String sub=token.substring(1);
 if(sub.length()==1){
 rule=new CharacterLiteral(sub.charAt(0));
+break;
 }else {
 rule=new StringLiteral(sub);
 }
 break;
 default :
 
 throw new IllegalArgumentException("Illegal pattern component: "+token);
 }
 rules.add(rule);
 }
 return rules;
 }

 }else {

 protected List<Rule> parsePattern(){
 DateFormatSymbols symbols=new DateFormatSymbols(mLocale);
 List<Rule> rules=new ArrayList<Rule>();
 String[] ERAs=symbols.getEras();
 String[] months=symbols.getMonths();
 String[] shortMonths=symbols.getShortMonths();
 String[] weekdays=symbols.getWeekdays();
 String[] shortWeekdays=symbols.getShortWeekdays();
 String[] AmPmStrings=symbols.getAmPmStrings();
 int length=mPattern.length();
 int[] indexRef=new int[1];
 for(int i=0;i<length;i++){
 indexRef[0]=i;
 String token=parseToken(mPattern,indexRef);
 i=indexRef[0];
 int tokenLen=token.length();
 if(tokenLen==0){
 break;
 }
 Rule rule;
 char c=token.charAt(0);
 switch (c){
 case 'G' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.ERA,ERAs);
 break;
 case 'y' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.YEAR,tokenLen);
 }else {
 rule=TwoDigitYearField.INSTANCE;
 }
 break;
 case 'M' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.MONTH,months);
 }else {
 if(tokenLen==3){
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.MONTH,shortMonths);
 }else {
 if(tokenLen==2){
 rule=TwoDigitMonthField.INSTANCE;
 }else {
 rule=UnpaddedMonthField.INSTANCE;
 }
 }
 }
 break;
 case 'd' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'h' :
 
 rule=new TwelveHourField(selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR,tokenLen));
 break;
 case 'H' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR_OF_DAY,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'm' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.MINUTE,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 's' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.SECOND,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'S' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.MILLISECOND,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'E' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.DAY_OF_WEEK,tokenLen<4?shortWeekdays:weekdays);
 break;
 case 'D' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_YEAR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'F' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_WEEK_IN_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'w' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.WEEK_OF_YEAR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'W' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.WEEK_OF_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'a' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.AM_PM,AmPmStrings);
 break;
 case 'k' :
 
 rule=new TwentyFourHourField(selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR_OF_DAY,tokenLen));
 break;
 case 'K' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'z' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=new TimeZoneNameRule(mTimeZone,mTimeZoneForced,mLocale,TimeZone.LONG);
 }else {
 rule=new TimeZoneNameRule(mTimeZone,mTimeZoneForced,mLocale,TimeZone.SHORT);
 }
 break;
 case 'Z' :
 
 if(tokenLen==1){
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_NO_COLON;
 }else {
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_COLON;
 }
 break;

 if(sub.length()==1){
 rule=new CharacterLiteral(sub.charAt(0));
 }else {
 rule=new StringLiteral(sub);
 }
 break;

 protected List<Rule> parsePattern(){
 DateFormatSymbols symbols=new DateFormatSymbols(mLocale);
 List<Rule> rules=new ArrayList<Rule>();
 String[] ERAs=symbols.getEras();
 String[] months=symbols.getMonths();
-String[] shortMonths=symbols.getShortMonths();
-String[] weekdays=symbols.getWeekdays();
+ final String[] shortMonths=symbols.getShortMonths();
+ final String[] weekdays=symbols.getWeekdays();
 String[] shortWeekdays=symbols.getShortWeekdays();
 String[] AmPmStrings=symbols.getAmPmStrings();
 int length=mPattern.length();
 int[] indexRef=new int[1];
 for(int i=0;i<length;i++){
 indexRef[0]=i;
 String token=parseToken(mPattern,indexRef);
 i=indexRef[0];
 int tokenLen=token.length();
 if(tokenLen==0){
 break;
 }
 Rule rule;
 char c=token.charAt(0);
 switch (c){
 case 'G' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.ERA,ERAs);
 break;
 case 'y' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.YEAR,tokenLen);
 }else {
 rule=TwoDigitYearField.INSTANCE;
 }
 break;
 case 'M' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.MONTH,months);
 }else {
 if(tokenLen==3){
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.MONTH,shortMonths);
 }else {
 if(tokenLen==2){
 rule=TwoDigitMonthField.INSTANCE;
 }else {
 rule=UnpaddedMonthField.INSTANCE;
 }
 }
 }
 break;
 case 'd' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'h' :
 
 rule=new TwelveHourField(selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR,tokenLen));
 break;
 case 'H' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR_OF_DAY,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'm' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.MINUTE,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 's' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.SECOND,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'S' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.MILLISECOND,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'E' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.DAY_OF_WEEK,tokenLen<4?shortWeekdays:weekdays);
 break;
 case 'D' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_YEAR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'F' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_WEEK_IN_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'w' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.WEEK_OF_YEAR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'W' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.WEEK_OF_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'a' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.AM_PM,AmPmStrings);
 break;
 case 'k' :
 
 rule=new TwentyFourHourField(selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR_OF_DAY,tokenLen));
 break;
 case 'K' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'z' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=new TimeZoneNameRule(mTimeZone,mTimeZoneForced,mLocale,TimeZone.LONG);
 }else {
 rule=new TimeZoneNameRule(mTimeZone,mTimeZoneForced,mLocale,TimeZone.SHORT);
 }
 break;
 case 'Z' :
 
 if(tokenLen==1){
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_NO_COLON;
 }else {
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_COLON;
 }
 break;
 case '\'' :
 
 String sub=token.substring(1);
 if(sub.length()==1){
 rule=new CharacterLiteral(sub.charAt(0));
 }else {
 rule=new StringLiteral(sub);
 }
 break;
 default :
 
 throw new IllegalArgumentException("Illegal pattern component: "+token);
 }
 rules.add(rule);
 }
 return rules;
 }

 protected List<Rule> parsePattern(){
 DateFormatSymbols symbols=new DateFormatSymbols(mLocale);
 List<Rule> rules=new ArrayList<Rule>();
 String[] ERAs=symbols.getEras();
 String[] months=symbols.getMonths();
 String[] shortMonths=symbols.getShortMonths();
 String[] weekdays=symbols.getWeekdays();
 String[] shortWeekdays=symbols.getShortWeekdays();

 int length=mPattern.length();
 int[] indexRef=new int[1];
 for(int i=0;i<length;i++){
 indexRef[0]=i;
 String token=parseToken(mPattern,indexRef);
 i=indexRef[0];
 int tokenLen=token.length();
 if(tokenLen==0){
 break;
 }
 Rule rule;
 char c=token.charAt(0);
 switch (c){
 case 'G' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.ERA,ERAs);
 break;
 case 'y' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.YEAR,tokenLen);
 }else {
 rule=TwoDigitYearField.INSTANCE;
 }
 break;
 case 'M' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.MONTH,months);
 }else {
 if(tokenLen==3){
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.MONTH,shortMonths);
 }else {
 if(tokenLen==2){
+this.parsePattern();
 rule=TwoDigitMonthField.INSTANCE;
 }else {
 rule=UnpaddedMonthField.INSTANCE;
 }
 }
 }
 break;
 case 'd' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'h' :
 
 rule=new TwelveHourField(selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR,tokenLen));
 break;
 case 'H' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR_OF_DAY,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'm' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.MINUTE,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 's' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.SECOND,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'S' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.MILLISECOND,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'E' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.DAY_OF_WEEK,tokenLen<4?shortWeekdays:weekdays);
 break;
 case 'D' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_YEAR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'F' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_WEEK_IN_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'w' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.WEEK_OF_YEAR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'W' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.WEEK_OF_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'a' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.AM_PM,AmPmStrings);
 break;
 case 'k' :
 
 rule=new TwentyFourHourField(selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR_OF_DAY,tokenLen));
 break;
 case 'K' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'z' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=new TimeZoneNameRule(mTimeZone,mTimeZoneForced,mLocale,TimeZone.LONG);
 }else {
 rule=new TimeZoneNameRule(mTimeZone,mTimeZoneForced,mLocale,TimeZone.SHORT);
 }
 break;
 case 'Z' :
 
 if(tokenLen==1){
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_NO_COLON;
 }else {
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_COLON;
 }
 break;
 case '\'' :
 
 String sub=token.substring(1);
 if(sub.length()==1){
 rule=new CharacterLiteral(sub.charAt(0));
 }else {
 rule=new StringLiteral(sub);
 }
 break;
 default :
 
 throw new IllegalArgumentException("Illegal pattern component: "+token);
 }
 rules.add(rule);
 }
 return rules;
 }

 }else {
 rule=new TimeZoneNameRule(mTimeZone,mTimeZoneForced,mLocale,TimeZone.SHORT);
 }
 break;
 case 'Z' :

 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_NO_COLON;
 }else {
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_COLON;
 }
 break;
 case '\'' :

 if(sub.length()==1){
 rule=new CharacterLiteral(sub.charAt(0));
 }else {
 rule=new StringLiteral(sub);
 }
 break;
 default :
 
 throw new IllegalArgumentException("Illegal pattern component: "+token);
 }
 rules.add(rule);
 }

 }else {

 }
 break;

 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_COLON;
 }
 break;

 }else {
 rule=new StringLiteral(sub);
 }
 break;
 default :
 
 throw new IllegalArgumentException("Illegal pattern component: "+token);
 }
 rules.add(rule);
 }

 protected List<Rule> parsePattern(){
 DateFormatSymbols symbols=new DateFormatSymbols(mLocale);
 List<Rule> rules=new ArrayList<Rule>();
 String[] ERAs=symbols.getEras();
 String[] months=symbols.getMonths();
 String[] shortMonths=symbols.getShortMonths();
 String[] weekdays=symbols.getWeekdays();
 String[] shortWeekdays=symbols.getShortWeekdays();
 String[] AmPmStrings=symbols.getAmPmStrings();
 int length=mPattern.length();
 int[] indexRef=new int[1];
 for(int i=0;i<length;i++){
 indexRef[0]=i;
 String token=parseToken(mPattern,indexRef);
 i=indexRef[0];
 int tokenLen=token.length();
 if(tokenLen==0){
 break;
 }
 Rule rule;
 char c=token.charAt(0);
 switch (c){
 case 'G' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.ERA,ERAs);
 break;
 case 'y' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.YEAR,tokenLen);
 }else {
 rule=TwoDigitYearField.INSTANCE;
 }
 break;
 case 'M' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.MONTH,months);
 }else {
 if(tokenLen==3){
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.MONTH,shortMonths);
 }else {
 if(tokenLen==2){
 rule=TwoDigitMonthField.INSTANCE;
 }else {
 rule=UnpaddedMonthField.INSTANCE;
 }
 }
 }
 break;
 case 'd' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'h' :
 
 rule=new TwelveHourField(selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR,tokenLen));
 break;
 case 'H' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR_OF_DAY,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'm' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.MINUTE,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 's' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.SECOND,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'S' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.MILLISECOND,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'E' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.DAY_OF_WEEK,tokenLen<4?shortWeekdays:weekdays);
 break;
 case 'D' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_YEAR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'F' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_WEEK_IN_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'w' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.WEEK_OF_YEAR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'W' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.WEEK_OF_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'a' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.AM_PM,AmPmStrings);
 break;
 case 'k' :
 
 rule=new TwentyFourHourField(selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR_OF_DAY,tokenLen));
 break;
 case 'K' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'z' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=new TimeZoneNameRule(mTimeZone,mTimeZoneForced,mLocale,TimeZone.LONG);
 }else {
 rule=new TimeZoneNameRule(mTimeZone,mTimeZoneForced,mLocale,TimeZone.SHORT);
 }
 break;
 case 'Z' :
 
 if(tokenLen==1){
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_NO_COLON;
 }else {
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_COLON;
 }
 break;
 case '\'' :
 
 String sub=token.substring(1);
 if(sub.length()==1){
 rule=new CharacterLiteral(sub.charAt(0));
 }else {
 rule=new StringLiteral(sub);
+i--;
 }
 break;
 default :
 
 throw new IllegalArgumentException("Illegal pattern component: "+token);
 }
 rules.add(rule);
 }
 return rules;
 }

 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_COLON;
 }
 break;
 case '\'' :
 
 String sub=token.substring(1);
 if(sub.length()==1){
 rule=new CharacterLiteral(sub.charAt(0));
+break;
 }else {
 rule=new StringLiteral(sub);
 }
 break;
 default :
 
 throw new IllegalArgumentException("Illegal pattern component: "+token);
 }
 rules.add(rule);
 }
 return rules;
 }

 break;

 break;

 break;

 }else {
 rule=new StringLiteral(sub);
 }
 break;
 default :

 protected List<Rule> parsePattern(){
 DateFormatSymbols symbols=new DateFormatSymbols(mLocale);
 List<Rule> rules=new ArrayList<Rule>();
 String[] ERAs=symbols.getEras();
 String[] months=symbols.getMonths();
 String[] shortMonths=symbols.getShortMonths();
 String[] weekdays=symbols.getWeekdays();
 String[] shortWeekdays=symbols.getShortWeekdays();
 String[] AmPmStrings=symbols.getAmPmStrings();
 int length=mPattern.length();
 int[] indexRef=new int[1];
 for(int i=0;i<length;i++){
 indexRef[0]=i;
 String token=parseToken(mPattern,indexRef);
 i=indexRef[0];
 int tokenLen=token.length();
 if(tokenLen==0){
 break;
 }
 Rule rule;
 char c=token.charAt(0);
 switch (c){
 case 'G' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.ERA,ERAs);
 break;
 case 'y' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.YEAR,tokenLen);
 }else {
 rule=TwoDigitYearField.INSTANCE;
 }
 break;
 case 'M' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.MONTH,months);
 }else {
 if(tokenLen==3){
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.MONTH,shortMonths);
 }else {
 if(tokenLen==2){
 rule=TwoDigitMonthField.INSTANCE;
 }else {
 rule=UnpaddedMonthField.INSTANCE;
 }
 }
+break;
 }
 break;
 case 'd' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'h' :
 
 rule=new TwelveHourField(selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR,tokenLen));
 break;
 case 'H' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR_OF_DAY,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'm' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.MINUTE,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 's' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.SECOND,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'S' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.MILLISECOND,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'E' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.DAY_OF_WEEK,tokenLen<4?shortWeekdays:weekdays);
 break;
 case 'D' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_YEAR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'F' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_WEEK_IN_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'w' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.WEEK_OF_YEAR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'W' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.WEEK_OF_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'a' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.AM_PM,AmPmStrings);
 break;
 case 'k' :
 
 rule=new TwentyFourHourField(selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR_OF_DAY,tokenLen));
 break;
 case 'K' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'z' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=new TimeZoneNameRule(mTimeZone,mTimeZoneForced,mLocale,TimeZone.LONG);
 }else {
 rule=new TimeZoneNameRule(mTimeZone,mTimeZoneForced,mLocale,TimeZone.SHORT);
 }
 break;
 case 'Z' :
 
 if(tokenLen==1){
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_NO_COLON;
 }else {
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_COLON;
 }
 break;
 case '\'' :
 
 String sub=token.substring(1);
 if(sub.length()==1){
 rule=new CharacterLiteral(sub.charAt(0));
+break;
 }else {
 rule=new StringLiteral(sub);
 }
 break;
 default :
 
 throw new IllegalArgumentException("Illegal pattern component: "+token);
 }
 rules.add(rule);
 }
 return rules;
 }

 case 'a' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.AM_PM,AmPmStrings);
 break;
 case 'k' :
 
 rule=new TwentyFourHourField(selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR_OF_DAY,tokenLen));
 break;
 case 'K' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'z' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=new TimeZoneNameRule(mTimeZone,mTimeZoneForced,mLocale,TimeZone.LONG);
 }else {
 rule=new TimeZoneNameRule(mTimeZone,mTimeZoneForced,mLocale,TimeZone.SHORT);
 }
 break;
 case 'Z' :
 
 if(tokenLen==1){
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_NO_COLON;
 }else {
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_COLON;
 }
 break;
 case '\'' :
 
 String sub=token.substring(1);
 if(sub.length()==1){
 rule=new CharacterLiteral(sub.charAt(0));
 }else {
 rule=new StringLiteral(sub);
 }
 break;
 default :
 
 throw new IllegalArgumentException("Illegal pattern component: "+token);
 }
 rules.add(rule);
 }
 return rules;
 }

 rule=new TextField(Calendar.DAY_OF_WEEK,tokenLen<4?shortWeekdays:weekdays);
 break;
 case 'D' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_YEAR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'F' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_WEEK_IN_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'w' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.WEEK_OF_YEAR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'W' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.WEEK_OF_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'a' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.AM_PM,AmPmStrings);
 break;
 case 'k' :
 
 rule=new TwentyFourHourField(selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR_OF_DAY,tokenLen));
 break;
 case 'K' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'z' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=new TimeZoneNameRule(mTimeZone,mTimeZoneForced,mLocale,TimeZone.LONG);
 }else {
 rule=new TimeZoneNameRule(mTimeZone,mTimeZoneForced,mLocale,TimeZone.SHORT);
 }
 break;
 case 'Z' :
 
 if(tokenLen==1){
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_NO_COLON;
 }else {
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_COLON;
 }
 break;
 case '\'' :
 
 String sub=token.substring(1);
 if(sub.length()==1){
 rule=new CharacterLiteral(sub.charAt(0));
 }else {
 rule=new StringLiteral(sub);
 }
 break;
 default :
 
 throw new IllegalArgumentException("Illegal pattern component: "+token);
 }
 rules.add(rule);
 }
 return rules;
 }

 protected List<Rule> parsePattern(){
 DateFormatSymbols symbols=new DateFormatSymbols(mLocale);
 List<Rule> rules=new ArrayList<Rule>();
-String[] ERAs=symbols.getEras();
-String[] months=symbols.getMonths();
+ final String[] ERAs=symbols.getEras();
+ final String[] months=symbols.getMonths();
 String[] shortMonths=symbols.getShortMonths();
 String[] weekdays=symbols.getWeekdays();
-String[] shortWeekdays=symbols.getShortWeekdays();
+ final String[] shortWeekdays=symbols.getShortWeekdays();
 String[] AmPmStrings=symbols.getAmPmStrings();
 int length=mPattern.length();
 int[] indexRef=new int[1];
 for(int i=0;i<length;i++){
 indexRef[0]=i;
 String token=parseToken(mPattern,indexRef);
 i=indexRef[0];
 int tokenLen=token.length();
 if(tokenLen==0){
 break;
 }
 Rule rule;
 char c=token.charAt(0);
 switch (c){
 case 'G' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.ERA,ERAs);
 break;
 case 'y' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.YEAR,tokenLen);
 }else {
 rule=TwoDigitYearField.INSTANCE;
 }
 break;
 case 'M' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.MONTH,months);
 }else {
 if(tokenLen==3){
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.MONTH,shortMonths);
 }else {
 if(tokenLen==2){
 rule=TwoDigitMonthField.INSTANCE;
 }else {
 rule=UnpaddedMonthField.INSTANCE;
 }
 }
 }
 break;
 case 'd' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'h' :
 
 rule=new TwelveHourField(selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR,tokenLen));
 break;
 case 'H' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR_OF_DAY,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'm' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.MINUTE,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 's' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.SECOND,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'S' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.MILLISECOND,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'E' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.DAY_OF_WEEK,tokenLen<4?shortWeekdays:weekdays);
 break;
 case 'D' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_YEAR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'F' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_WEEK_IN_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'w' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.WEEK_OF_YEAR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'W' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.WEEK_OF_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'a' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.AM_PM,AmPmStrings);
 break;
 case 'k' :
 
 rule=new TwentyFourHourField(selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR_OF_DAY,tokenLen));
 break;
 case 'K' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'z' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=new TimeZoneNameRule(mTimeZone,mTimeZoneForced,mLocale,TimeZone.LONG);
 }else {
 rule=new TimeZoneNameRule(mTimeZone,mTimeZoneForced,mLocale,TimeZone.SHORT);
 }
 break;
 case 'Z' :
 
 if(tokenLen==1){
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_NO_COLON;
 }else {
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_COLON;
 }
 break;
 case '\'' :
 
 String sub=token.substring(1);
 if(sub.length()==1){
 rule=new CharacterLiteral(sub.charAt(0));
 }else {
 rule=new StringLiteral(sub);
 }
 break;
 default :
 
 throw new IllegalArgumentException("Illegal pattern component: "+token);
 }
 rules.add(rule);
 }
 return rules;
 }

 rule=new TimeZoneNameRule(mTimeZone,mTimeZoneForced,mLocale,TimeZone.SHORT);
 }
 break;
 case 'Z' :
 
 if(tokenLen==1){
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_NO_COLON;
 }else {
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_COLON;
 }
 break;
 case '\'' :
 
 String sub=token.substring(1);
 if(sub.length()==1){
 rule=new CharacterLiteral(sub.charAt(0));
 }else {
 rule=new StringLiteral(sub);
 }
 break;
 default :
 
 throw new IllegalArgumentException("Illegal pattern component: "+token);
 }
 rules.add(rule);
 }
 return rules;
 }

 i=indexRef[0];

 break;
 }

 switch (c){
 case 'G' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.ERA,ERAs);
 break;
 case 'y' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.YEAR,tokenLen);
 }else {
 rule=TwoDigitYearField.INSTANCE;
 }
 break;
 case 'M' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.MONTH,months);
 }else {
 if(tokenLen==3){
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.MONTH,shortMonths);
 }else {
 if(tokenLen==2){
 rule=TwoDigitMonthField.INSTANCE;
 }else {
 rule=UnpaddedMonthField.INSTANCE;
 }
 }
 }
 break;
 case 'd' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'h' :
 
 rule=new TwelveHourField(selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR,tokenLen));
 break;
 case 'H' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR_OF_DAY,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'm' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.MINUTE,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 's' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.SECOND,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'S' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.MILLISECOND,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'E' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.DAY_OF_WEEK,tokenLen<4?shortWeekdays:weekdays);
 break;

 break;

 break;

 break;

 break;

 }else {
 rule=new TimeZoneNameRule(mTimeZone,mTimeZoneForced,mLocale,TimeZone.SHORT);
 }
 break;

 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_NO_COLON;
 }else {
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_COLON;

 }else {
+int a=0;
 rule=new StringLiteral(sub);
 }
 break;
 default :
 
 throw new IllegalArgumentException("Illegal pattern component: "+token);
 }

 }
 return rules;

 case 'k' :

 break;

 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR,tokenLen);
 break;

 }else {
 rule=new TimeZoneNameRule(mTimeZone,mTimeZoneForced,mLocale,TimeZone.SHORT);
 }
 break;
 case 'Z' :

 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_NO_COLON;
 }else {
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_COLON;
 }
 break;
 case '\'' :

 if(sub.length()==1){

 }else {
 rule=new StringLiteral(sub);
 }
 break;
 default :
 
 throw new IllegalArgumentException("Illegal pattern component: "+token);
 }
 rules.add(rule);
 }

 case 'H' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR_OF_DAY,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'm' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.MINUTE,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 's' :
 
-rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.SECOND,tokenLen);
+rule=this.selectNumberRule(Calendar.SECOND,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'S' :
 
-rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.MILLISECOND,tokenLen);
+rule=this.selectNumberRule(Calendar.MILLISECOND,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'E' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.DAY_OF_WEEK,tokenLen<4?shortWeekdays:weekdays);
 break;
 case 'D' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_YEAR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'F' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_WEEK_IN_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'w' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.WEEK_OF_YEAR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'W' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.WEEK_OF_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'a' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.AM_PM,AmPmStrings);
 break;
 case 'k' :

 break;
 case 'K' :
 
-rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR,tokenLen);
+rule=this.selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'z' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=new TimeZoneNameRule(mTimeZone,mTimeZoneForced,mLocale,TimeZone.LONG);
 }else {
 rule=new TimeZoneNameRule(mTimeZone,mTimeZoneForced,mLocale,TimeZone.SHORT);
 }
 break;
 case 'Z' :
 
 if(tokenLen==1){
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_NO_COLON;
 }else {
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_COLON;
 }
 break;
 case '\'' :
 
 String sub=token.substring(1);
 if(sub.length()==1){
 rule=new CharacterLiteral(sub.charAt(0));
 }else {
 rule=new StringLiteral(sub);
 }
 break;
 default :
 
 throw new IllegalArgumentException("Illegal pattern component: "+token);
 }
 rules.add(rule);
 }
 return rules;
 }

 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR_OF_DAY,tokenLen);
 break;

 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.MINUTE,tokenLen);
 break;

+rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.SECOND,Math.round(tokenLen));
 break;

 break;

 }else {

 break;

 break;

 protected List<Rule> parsePattern(){
 DateFormatSymbols symbols=new DateFormatSymbols(mLocale);
 List<Rule> rules=new ArrayList<Rule>();
 String[] ERAs=symbols.getEras();
 String[] months=symbols.getMonths();
 String[] shortMonths=symbols.getShortMonths();
 String[] weekdays=symbols.getWeekdays();
 String[] shortWeekdays=symbols.getShortWeekdays();
 String[] AmPmStrings=symbols.getAmPmStrings();
 int length=mPattern.length();
 int[] indexRef=new int[1];
 for(int i=0;i<length;i++){
 indexRef[0]=i;
 String token=parseToken(mPattern,indexRef);
 i=indexRef[0];
 int tokenLen=token.length();
 if(tokenLen==0){
 break;
 }
 Rule rule;
 char c=token.charAt(0);
 switch (c){
 case 'G' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.ERA,ERAs);
 break;
 case 'y' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
-rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.YEAR,tokenLen);
+rule=null;
 }else {
 rule=TwoDigitYearField.INSTANCE;
 }
 break;
 case 'M' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.MONTH,months);
 }else {
 if(tokenLen==3){
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.MONTH,shortMonths);
 }else {
 if(tokenLen==2){
 rule=TwoDigitMonthField.INSTANCE;
 }else {
 rule=UnpaddedMonthField.INSTANCE;
 }
 }
 }
 break;
 case 'd' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'h' :
 
 rule=new TwelveHourField(selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR,tokenLen));
 break;
 case 'H' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR_OF_DAY,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'm' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.MINUTE,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 's' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.SECOND,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'S' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.MILLISECOND,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'E' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.DAY_OF_WEEK,tokenLen<4?shortWeekdays:weekdays);
 break;
 case 'D' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_YEAR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'F' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_WEEK_IN_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'w' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.WEEK_OF_YEAR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'W' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.WEEK_OF_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'a' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.AM_PM,AmPmStrings);
 break;
 case 'k' :
 
 rule=new TwentyFourHourField(selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR_OF_DAY,tokenLen));
 break;
 case 'K' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'z' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=new TimeZoneNameRule(mTimeZone,mTimeZoneForced,mLocale,TimeZone.LONG);
 }else {
 rule=new TimeZoneNameRule(mTimeZone,mTimeZoneForced,mLocale,TimeZone.SHORT);
 }
 break;
 case 'Z' :
 
 if(tokenLen==1){
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_NO_COLON;
 }else {
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_COLON;
 }
 break;
 case '\'' :
 
 String sub=token.substring(1);
 if(sub.length()==1){
 rule=new CharacterLiteral(sub.charAt(0));
 }else {
 rule=new StringLiteral(sub);
 }
 break;
 default :
 
 throw new IllegalArgumentException("Illegal pattern component: "+token);
 }
 rules.add(rule);
 }
 return rules;
 }

 DateFormatSymbols symbols=new DateFormatSymbols(mLocale);
 List<Rule> rules=new ArrayList<Rule>();
 String[] ERAs=symbols.getEras();
 String[] months=symbols.getMonths();
 String[] shortMonths=symbols.getShortMonths();
 String[] weekdays=symbols.getWeekdays();
 String[] shortWeekdays=symbols.getShortWeekdays();
 String[] AmPmStrings=symbols.getAmPmStrings();
 int length=mPattern.length();
 int[] indexRef=new int[1];
 for(int i=0;i<length;i++){
 indexRef[0]=i;
 String token=parseToken(mPattern,indexRef);
 i=indexRef[0];
 int tokenLen=token.length();
 if(tokenLen==0){
 break;
 }
 Rule rule;
 char c=token.charAt(0);
 switch (c){
 case 'G' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.ERA,ERAs);
 break;
 case 'y' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.YEAR,tokenLen);
 }else {
 rule=TwoDigitYearField.INSTANCE;
 }
 break;
 case 'M' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.MONTH,months);
 }else {
 if(tokenLen==3){
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.MONTH,shortMonths);
 }else {
 if(tokenLen==2){
 rule=TwoDigitMonthField.INSTANCE;
 }else {
 rule=UnpaddedMonthField.INSTANCE;
 }
+int indexSelection=0;
 }
 }
 break;
 case 'd' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'h' :
 
 rule=new TwelveHourField(selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR,tokenLen));
 break;
 case 'H' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR_OF_DAY,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'm' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.MINUTE,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 's' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.SECOND,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'S' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.MILLISECOND,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'E' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.DAY_OF_WEEK,tokenLen<4?shortWeekdays:weekdays);
 break;
 case 'D' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_YEAR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'F' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_WEEK_IN_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'w' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.WEEK_OF_YEAR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'W' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.WEEK_OF_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'a' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.AM_PM,AmPmStrings);
 break;
 case 'k' :
 
 rule=new TwentyFourHourField(selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR_OF_DAY,tokenLen));
 break;
 case 'K' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'z' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=new TimeZoneNameRule(mTimeZone,mTimeZoneForced,mLocale,TimeZone.LONG);
 }else {
 rule=new TimeZoneNameRule(mTimeZone,mTimeZoneForced,mLocale,TimeZone.SHORT);
 }
 break;
 case 'Z' :
 
 if(tokenLen==1){
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_NO_COLON;
 }else {
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_COLON;
 }
 break;
 case '\'' :
 
 String sub=token.substring(1);
 if(sub.length()==1){
 rule=new CharacterLiteral(sub.charAt(0));
 }else {
 rule=new StringLiteral(sub);
 }
 break;
 default :
 
 throw new IllegalArgumentException("Illegal pattern component: "+token);
 }
 rules.add(rule);
 }
 return rules;
 }

 break;

 }else {

 }
 break;

 }else {

 }

 }else {
 rule=new StringLiteral(sub);
 }
 break;
 default :
 
 throw new IllegalArgumentException("Illegal pattern component: "+token);
 }
 rules.add(rule);
 }

 protected List<Rule> parsePattern(){
 DateFormatSymbols symbols=new DateFormatSymbols(mLocale);
 List<Rule> rules=new ArrayList<Rule>();
 String[] ERAs=symbols.getEras();
 String[] months=symbols.getMonths();
 String[] shortMonths=symbols.getShortMonths();
 String[] weekdays=symbols.getWeekdays();
 String[] shortWeekdays=symbols.getShortWeekdays();
 String[] AmPmStrings=symbols.getAmPmStrings();
 int length=mPattern.length();
 int[] indexRef=new int[1];
 for(int i=0;i<length;i++){
 indexRef[0]=i;
 String token=parseToken(mPattern,indexRef);
 i=indexRef[0];
 int tokenLen=token.length();
 if(tokenLen==0){
 break;
 }
 Rule rule;
 char c=token.charAt(0);
 switch (c){
 case 'G' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.ERA,ERAs);
 break;
 case 'y' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.YEAR,tokenLen);
 }else {
 rule=TwoDigitYearField.INSTANCE;
 }
 break;
 case 'M' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.MONTH,months);
 }else {
 if(tokenLen==3){
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.MONTH,shortMonths);
 }else {
 if(tokenLen==2){
 rule=TwoDigitMonthField.INSTANCE;
 }else {
 rule=UnpaddedMonthField.INSTANCE;
 }
 }
 }
 break;
 case 'd' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'h' :
 
 rule=new TwelveHourField(selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR,tokenLen));
 break;
 case 'H' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR_OF_DAY,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'm' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.MINUTE,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 's' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.SECOND,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'S' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.MILLISECOND,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'E' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.DAY_OF_WEEK,tokenLen<4?shortWeekdays:weekdays);
 break;
 case 'D' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_YEAR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'F' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_WEEK_IN_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'w' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.WEEK_OF_YEAR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'W' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.WEEK_OF_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'a' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.AM_PM,AmPmStrings);
 break;
 case 'k' :
 
 rule=new TwentyFourHourField(selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR_OF_DAY,tokenLen));
 break;
 case 'K' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'z' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=new TimeZoneNameRule(mTimeZone,mTimeZoneForced,mLocale,TimeZone.LONG);
 }else {
 rule=new TimeZoneNameRule(mTimeZone,mTimeZoneForced,mLocale,TimeZone.SHORT);
 }
 break;
 case 'Z' :
 
 if(tokenLen==1){
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_NO_COLON;
 }else {
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_COLON;
 }
 break;
 case '\'' :
 
 String sub=token.substring(1);
 if(sub.length()==1){
 rule=new CharacterLiteral(sub.charAt(0));
 }else {
 rule=new StringLiteral(sub);
 }
 break;
 default :
 
 throw new IllegalArgumentException("Illegal pattern component: "+token);
 }
 rules.add(rule);
+boolean Calendar=true;
 }
 return rules;

 }else {
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_COLON;
 }

 if(sub.length()==1){
 rule=new CharacterLiteral(sub.charAt(0));
 }else {
 rule=new StringLiteral(sub);
 }
 break;
 default :
 
 throw new IllegalArgumentException("Illegal pattern component: "+token);
 }
 rules.add(rule);
 }

 case 'G' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.ERA,ERAs);
 break;
 case 'y' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.YEAR,tokenLen);
 }else {
 rule=TwoDigitYearField.INSTANCE;
 }
 break;
 case 'M' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.MONTH,months);
 }else {
 if(tokenLen==3){
+if(shortMonths==null){
+return null;
+}
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.MONTH,shortMonths);
 }else {
 if(tokenLen==2){
 rule=TwoDigitMonthField.INSTANCE;
 }else {
 rule=UnpaddedMonthField.INSTANCE;
 }
 }
 }
 break;
 case 'd' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'h' :
 
 rule=new TwelveHourField(selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR,tokenLen));
 break;
 case 'H' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR_OF_DAY,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'm' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.MINUTE,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 's' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.SECOND,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'S' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.MILLISECOND,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'E' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.DAY_OF_WEEK,tokenLen<4?shortWeekdays:weekdays);
 break;

 break;
 case 'F' :

 break;

 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.WEEK_OF_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'a' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.AM_PM,AmPmStrings);
 break;

 break;
 case 'K' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'z' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=new TimeZoneNameRule(mTimeZone,mTimeZoneForced,mLocale,TimeZone.LONG);
 }else {
 rule=new TimeZoneNameRule(mTimeZone,mTimeZoneForced,mLocale,TimeZone.SHORT);
 }
 break;
 case 'Z' :

 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_NO_COLON;
 }else {
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_COLON;
 }
 break;

 }else {
 rule=new StringLiteral(sub);
 }
 break;
 default :
 
 throw new IllegalArgumentException("Illegal pattern component: "+token);
 }
 rules.add(rule);
 }
 return rules;

 protected List<Rule> parsePattern(){
 DateFormatSymbols symbols=new DateFormatSymbols(mLocale);
+if(symbols==null){
+return null;
+}
 List<Rule> rules=new ArrayList<Rule>();
 String[] ERAs=symbols.getEras();
 String[] months=symbols.getMonths();
 String[] shortMonths=symbols.getShortMonths();
 String[] weekdays=symbols.getWeekdays();
 String[] shortWeekdays=symbols.getShortWeekdays();
 String[] AmPmStrings=symbols.getAmPmStrings();
 int length=mPattern.length();
 int[] indexRef=new int[1];
 for(int i=0;i<length;i++){
 indexRef[0]=i;
 String token=parseToken(mPattern,indexRef);
 i=indexRef[0];
 int tokenLen=token.length();
 if(tokenLen==0){
 break;
 }
 Rule rule;
 char c=token.charAt(0);
 switch (c){
 case 'G' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.ERA,ERAs);
 break;
 case 'y' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.YEAR,tokenLen);
 }else {
 rule=TwoDigitYearField.INSTANCE;
 }
 break;
 case 'M' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.MONTH,months);
 }else {
 if(tokenLen==3){
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.MONTH,shortMonths);
 }else {
 if(tokenLen==2){
 rule=TwoDigitMonthField.INSTANCE;
 }else {
 rule=UnpaddedMonthField.INSTANCE;
 }
 }
 }
 break;
 case 'd' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'h' :
 
 rule=new TwelveHourField(selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR,tokenLen));
 break;
 case 'H' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR_OF_DAY,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'm' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.MINUTE,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 's' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.SECOND,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'S' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.MILLISECOND,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'E' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.DAY_OF_WEEK,tokenLen<4?shortWeekdays:weekdays);
 break;
 case 'D' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_YEAR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'F' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_WEEK_IN_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'w' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.WEEK_OF_YEAR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'W' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.WEEK_OF_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'a' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.AM_PM,AmPmStrings);
 break;
 case 'k' :
 
 rule=new TwentyFourHourField(selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR_OF_DAY,tokenLen));
 break;
 case 'K' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'z' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=new TimeZoneNameRule(mTimeZone,mTimeZoneForced,mLocale,TimeZone.LONG);
 }else {
 rule=new TimeZoneNameRule(mTimeZone,mTimeZoneForced,mLocale,TimeZone.SHORT);
 }
 break;
 case 'Z' :
 
 if(tokenLen==1){
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_NO_COLON;
 }else {
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_COLON;
 }
 break;
 case '\'' :
 
 String sub=token.substring(1);
 if(sub.length()==1){
 rule=new CharacterLiteral(sub.charAt(0));
 }else {
 rule=new StringLiteral(sub);
 }
 break;
 default :
 
 throw new IllegalArgumentException("Illegal pattern component: "+token);
 }
 rules.add(rule);
 }
 return rules;

 break;

 }else {
 rule=new TimeZoneNameRule(mTimeZone,mTimeZoneForced,mLocale,TimeZone.SHORT);
 }
 break;
 case 'Z' :

 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_NO_COLON;
 }else {
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_COLON;
 }
 break;

 }else {
 rule=new StringLiteral(sub);
 }
 break;
 default :
 
 throw new IllegalArgumentException("Illegal pattern component: "+token);
 }
 rules.add(rule);
 }

 rule=new TextField(Calendar.MONTH,shortMonths);
 }else {
 if(tokenLen==2){
 rule=TwoDigitMonthField.INSTANCE;
 }else {

 }
 }
 }

 break;

 break;

 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.MINUTE,tokenLen);

 break;

 break;

 rule=new TextField(Calendar.ERA,ERAs);
 break;

 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.YEAR,tokenLen);
 }else {
 rule=TwoDigitYearField.INSTANCE;
 }
 break;

+rule=TwoDigitMonthField.INSTANCE;
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.MONTH,months);
 }else {
 if(tokenLen==3){
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.MONTH,shortMonths);
 }else {
 if(tokenLen==2){
 rule=TwoDigitMonthField.INSTANCE;
 }else {
 rule=UnpaddedMonthField.INSTANCE;
 }
 }
 }
 break;

 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;

 break;

 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR_OF_DAY,tokenLen);
 break;

 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.MINUTE,tokenLen);

 break;

 break;

 break;

 break;

 break;

 }else {
 rule=new TimeZoneNameRule(mTimeZone,mTimeZoneForced,mLocale,TimeZone.SHORT);
 }
 break;

 break;

 protected List<Rule> parsePattern(){
 DateFormatSymbols symbols=new DateFormatSymbols(mLocale);
 List<Rule> rules=new ArrayList<Rule>();
 String[] ERAs=symbols.getEras();
 String[] months=symbols.getMonths();
 String[] shortMonths=symbols.getShortMonths();
 String[] weekdays=symbols.getWeekdays();
 String[] shortWeekdays=symbols.getShortWeekdays();
 String[] AmPmStrings=symbols.getAmPmStrings();
 int length=mPattern.length();
 int[] indexRef=new int[1];
 for(int i=0;i<length;i++){
 indexRef[0]=i;
 String token=parseToken(mPattern,indexRef);
 i=indexRef[0];
 int tokenLen=token.length();
 if(tokenLen==0){
 break;
 }
 Rule rule;
 char c=token.charAt(0);
 switch (c){
 case 'G' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.ERA,ERAs);
 break;
 case 'y' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.YEAR,tokenLen);
 }else {
 rule=TwoDigitYearField.INSTANCE;
 }
 break;
 case 'M' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.MONTH,months);
 }else {
 if(tokenLen==3){
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.MONTH,shortMonths);
 }else {
 if(tokenLen==2){
 rule=TwoDigitMonthField.INSTANCE;
 }else {
+rule=UnpaddedMonthField.INSTANCE;
 rule=UnpaddedMonthField.INSTANCE;
 }
 }
 }
 break;
 case 'd' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'h' :
 
 rule=new TwelveHourField(selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR,tokenLen));
 break;
 case 'H' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR_OF_DAY,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'm' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.MINUTE,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 's' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.SECOND,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'S' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.MILLISECOND,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'E' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.DAY_OF_WEEK,tokenLen<4?shortWeekdays:weekdays);
 break;
 case 'D' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_YEAR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'F' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_WEEK_IN_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'w' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.WEEK_OF_YEAR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'W' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.WEEK_OF_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'a' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.AM_PM,AmPmStrings);
 break;
 case 'k' :
 
 rule=new TwentyFourHourField(selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR_OF_DAY,tokenLen));
 break;
 case 'K' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'z' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=new TimeZoneNameRule(mTimeZone,mTimeZoneForced,mLocale,TimeZone.LONG);
 }else {
 rule=new TimeZoneNameRule(mTimeZone,mTimeZoneForced,mLocale,TimeZone.SHORT);
 }
 break;
 case 'Z' :
 
 if(tokenLen==1){
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_NO_COLON;
 }else {
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_COLON;
 }
 break;
 case '\'' :
 
 String sub=token.substring(1);
 if(sub.length()==1){
 rule=new CharacterLiteral(sub.charAt(0));
 }else {
 rule=new StringLiteral(sub);
 }
 break;
 default :
 
 throw new IllegalArgumentException("Illegal pattern component: "+token);
 }
 rules.add(rule);
 }
 return rules;
 }

 }
 break;
 default :
 
 throw new IllegalArgumentException("Illegal pattern component: "+token);
 }
 rules.add(rule);
 }

 indexRef[0]=i;

 break;

 rule=new TextField(Calendar.ERA,ERAs);
 break;
 case 'y' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.YEAR,tokenLen);
 }else {
 rule=TwoDigitYearField.INSTANCE;
 }
 break;
 case 'M' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.MONTH,months);
 }else {
+rule=UnpaddedMonthField.INSTANCE;
 if(tokenLen==3){
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.MONTH,shortMonths);
 }else {
 if(tokenLen==2){
 rule=TwoDigitMonthField.INSTANCE;
 }else {
-rule=UnpaddedMonthField.INSTANCE;
 }
 }
 }
 break;

 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'h' :
 
 rule=new TwelveHourField(selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR,tokenLen));
 break;
 case 'H' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR_OF_DAY,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'm' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.MINUTE,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 's' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.SECOND,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'S' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.MILLISECOND,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'E' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.DAY_OF_WEEK,tokenLen<4?shortWeekdays:weekdays);
 break;
 case 'D' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_YEAR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'F' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_WEEK_IN_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;

 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.WEEK_OF_YEAR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'W' :

 break;

 rule=new TextField(Calendar.AM_PM,AmPmStrings);
 break;

 break;
 case 'K' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR,tokenLen);

 }else {
 rule=new TimeZoneNameRule(mTimeZone,mTimeZoneForced,mLocale,TimeZone.SHORT);
 }
 break;

 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_NO_COLON;
 }else {
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_COLON;
 }
 break;

 if(sub.length()==1){
 rule=new CharacterLiteral(sub.charAt(0));
 }else {
 rule=new StringLiteral(sub);
 }
 break;
 default :
 
 throw new IllegalArgumentException("Illegal pattern component: "+token);
 }
 rules.add(rule);
 }

 break;
 case 'E' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.DAY_OF_WEEK,tokenLen<4?shortWeekdays:weekdays);
 break;

 break;
 case 'K' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'z' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=new TimeZoneNameRule(mTimeZone,mTimeZoneForced,mLocale,TimeZone.LONG);
 }else {
 rule=new TimeZoneNameRule(mTimeZone,mTimeZoneForced,mLocale,TimeZone.SHORT);
 }
 break;
 case 'Z' :
 
 if(tokenLen==1){
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_NO_COLON;
 }else {
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_COLON;
 }
 break;
 case '\'' :

 rule=new CharacterLiteral(sub.charAt(0));
 }else {
 rule=new StringLiteral(sub);
 }
 break;
 default :
 
 throw new IllegalArgumentException("Illegal pattern component: "+token);
 }
 rules.add(rule);
 }
 return rules;

 protected List<Rule> parsePattern(){
 DateFormatSymbols symbols=new DateFormatSymbols(mLocale);
 List<Rule> rules=new ArrayList<Rule>();
 String[] ERAs=symbols.getEras();
 String[] months=symbols.getMonths();
 String[] shortMonths=symbols.getShortMonths();
 String[] weekdays=symbols.getWeekdays();
 String[] shortWeekdays=symbols.getShortWeekdays();
 String[] AmPmStrings=symbols.getAmPmStrings();
 int length=mPattern.length();
 int[] indexRef=new int[1];
 for(int i=0;i<length;i++){
 indexRef[0]=i;
 String token=parseToken(mPattern,indexRef);
 i=indexRef[0];
 int tokenLen=token.length();
 if(tokenLen==0){
 break;
 }
 Rule rule;
 char c=token.charAt(0);
 switch (c){
 case 'G' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.ERA,ERAs);
 break;
 case 'y' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.YEAR,tokenLen);
 }else {
 rule=TwoDigitYearField.INSTANCE;
 }
 break;
 case 'M' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.MONTH,months);
 }else {
 if(tokenLen==3){
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.MONTH,shortMonths);
 }else {
 if(tokenLen==2){
-rule=TwoDigitMonthField.INSTANCE;
 }else {
 rule=UnpaddedMonthField.INSTANCE;
 }
+rule=TwoDigitMonthField.INSTANCE;
 }
 }
 break;
 case 'd' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'h' :
 
 rule=new TwelveHourField(selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR,tokenLen));
 break;
 case 'H' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR_OF_DAY,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'm' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.MINUTE,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 's' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.SECOND,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'S' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.MILLISECOND,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'E' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.DAY_OF_WEEK,tokenLen<4?shortWeekdays:weekdays);
 break;
 case 'D' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_YEAR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'F' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_WEEK_IN_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'w' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.WEEK_OF_YEAR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'W' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.WEEK_OF_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'a' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.AM_PM,AmPmStrings);
 break;
 case 'k' :
 
 rule=new TwentyFourHourField(selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR_OF_DAY,tokenLen));
 break;
 case 'K' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'z' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=new TimeZoneNameRule(mTimeZone,mTimeZoneForced,mLocale,TimeZone.LONG);
 }else {
 rule=new TimeZoneNameRule(mTimeZone,mTimeZoneForced,mLocale,TimeZone.SHORT);
 }
 break;
 case 'Z' :
 
 if(tokenLen==1){
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_NO_COLON;
 }else {
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_COLON;
 }
 break;
 case '\'' :
 
 String sub=token.substring(1);
 if(sub.length()==1){
 rule=new CharacterLiteral(sub.charAt(0));
 }else {
 rule=new StringLiteral(sub);
 }
 break;
 default :
 
 throw new IllegalArgumentException("Illegal pattern component: "+token);
 }
 rules.add(rule);
 }
 return rules;
 }

 DateFormatSymbols symbols=new DateFormatSymbols(mLocale);
 List<Rule> rules=new ArrayList<Rule>();
 String[] ERAs=symbols.getEras();
 String[] months=symbols.getMonths();
 String[] shortMonths=symbols.getShortMonths();
 String[] weekdays=symbols.getWeekdays();
 String[] shortWeekdays=symbols.getShortWeekdays();
 String[] AmPmStrings=symbols.getAmPmStrings();
 int length=mPattern.length();
 int[] indexRef=new int[1];
 for(int i=0;i<length;i++){
 indexRef[0]=i;
 String token=parseToken(mPattern,indexRef);
-i=indexRef[0];
+i=-1;
 int tokenLen=token.length();
 if(tokenLen==0){
 break;
 }
 Rule rule;
 char c=token.charAt(0);
 switch (c){
 case 'G' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.ERA,ERAs);
 break;
 case 'y' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.YEAR,tokenLen);
 }else {
 rule=TwoDigitYearField.INSTANCE;
 }
 break;
 case 'M' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.MONTH,months);
 }else {
 if(tokenLen==3){
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.MONTH,shortMonths);
 }else {
 if(tokenLen==2){
 rule=TwoDigitMonthField.INSTANCE;
 }else {
 rule=UnpaddedMonthField.INSTANCE;
 }
 }
+i++;
 }
 break;
 case 'd' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'h' :
 
 rule=new TwelveHourField(selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR,tokenLen));
 break;
 case 'H' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR_OF_DAY,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'm' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.MINUTE,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 's' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.SECOND,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'S' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.MILLISECOND,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'E' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.DAY_OF_WEEK,tokenLen<4?shortWeekdays:weekdays);
 break;
 case 'D' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_YEAR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'F' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_WEEK_IN_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'w' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.WEEK_OF_YEAR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'W' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.WEEK_OF_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'a' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.AM_PM,AmPmStrings);
 break;
 case 'k' :
 
 rule=new TwentyFourHourField(selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR_OF_DAY,tokenLen));
 break;
 case 'K' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'z' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=new TimeZoneNameRule(mTimeZone,mTimeZoneForced,mLocale,TimeZone.LONG);
 }else {
 rule=new TimeZoneNameRule(mTimeZone,mTimeZoneForced,mLocale,TimeZone.SHORT);
 }
 break;
 case 'Z' :
 
 if(tokenLen==1){
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_NO_COLON;
 }else {
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_COLON;
 }
 break;
 case '\'' :
 
 String sub=token.substring(1);
 if(sub.length()==1){
 rule=new CharacterLiteral(sub.charAt(0));
 }else {
 rule=new StringLiteral(sub);
 }
 break;
 default :
 
 throw new IllegalArgumentException("Illegal pattern component: "+token);
 }
 rules.add(rule);
 }
 return rules;
 }

 protected List<Rule> parsePattern(){
 DateFormatSymbols symbols=new DateFormatSymbols(mLocale);
 List<Rule> rules=new ArrayList<Rule>();
 String[] ERAs=symbols.getEras();
 String[] months=symbols.getMonths();
 String[] shortMonths=symbols.getShortMonths();
 String[] weekdays=symbols.getWeekdays();
 String[] shortWeekdays=symbols.getShortWeekdays();
 String[] AmPmStrings=symbols.getAmPmStrings();
 int length=mPattern.length();
 int[] indexRef=new int[1];
 for(int i=0;i<length;i++){
 indexRef[0]=i;
 String token=parseToken(mPattern,indexRef);
 i=indexRef[0];
 int tokenLen=token.length();
 if(tokenLen==0){
 break;
 }
 Rule rule;
 char c=token.charAt(0);
 switch (c){
 case 'G' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.ERA,ERAs);
 break;
 case 'y' :
 
-if(tokenLen>=4){
+if(tokenLen>=4||"".equals(tokenLen)){
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.YEAR,tokenLen);
 }else {
 rule=TwoDigitYearField.INSTANCE;
 }
 break;
 case 'M' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.MONTH,months);
 }else {
 if(tokenLen==3){
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.MONTH,shortMonths);
 }else {
 if(tokenLen==2){
 rule=TwoDigitMonthField.INSTANCE;
 }else {
 rule=UnpaddedMonthField.INSTANCE;
 }
 }
 }
 break;
 case 'd' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'h' :
 
 rule=new TwelveHourField(selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR,tokenLen));
 break;
 case 'H' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR_OF_DAY,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'm' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.MINUTE,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 's' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.SECOND,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'S' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.MILLISECOND,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'E' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.DAY_OF_WEEK,tokenLen<4?shortWeekdays:weekdays);
 break;
 case 'D' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_YEAR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'F' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_WEEK_IN_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'w' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.WEEK_OF_YEAR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'W' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.WEEK_OF_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'a' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.AM_PM,AmPmStrings);
 break;
 case 'k' :
 
 rule=new TwentyFourHourField(selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR_OF_DAY,tokenLen));
 break;
 case 'K' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'z' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=new TimeZoneNameRule(mTimeZone,mTimeZoneForced,mLocale,TimeZone.LONG);
 }else {
 rule=new TimeZoneNameRule(mTimeZone,mTimeZoneForced,mLocale,TimeZone.SHORT);
 }
 break;
 case 'Z' :
 
 if(tokenLen==1){
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_NO_COLON;
 }else {
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_COLON;
 }
 break;
 case '\'' :
 
 String sub=token.substring(1);
 if(sub.length()==1){
 rule=new CharacterLiteral(sub.charAt(0));
 }else {
 rule=new StringLiteral(sub);
 }
 break;
 default :
 
 throw new IllegalArgumentException("Illegal pattern component: "+token);
 }
 rules.add(rule);
 }
 return rules;
 }

 }else {

 }
 break;
 default :

 }

 String[] ERAs=symbols.getEras();
 String[] months=symbols.getMonths();
 String[] shortMonths=symbols.getShortMonths();
 String[] weekdays=symbols.getWeekdays();
 String[] shortWeekdays=symbols.getShortWeekdays();
 String[] AmPmStrings=symbols.getAmPmStrings();
 int length=mPattern.length();
 int[] indexRef=new int[1];
 for(int i=0;i<length;i++){
 indexRef[0]=i;
 String token=parseToken(mPattern,indexRef);
 i=indexRef[0];
 int tokenLen=token.length();
 if(tokenLen==0){
 break;
 }
 Rule rule;
 char c=token.charAt(0);
 switch (c){
 case 'G' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.ERA,ERAs);
 break;
 case 'y' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.YEAR,tokenLen);
 }else {
 rule=TwoDigitYearField.INSTANCE;
 }
 break;
 case 'M' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.MONTH,months);
 }else {
 if(tokenLen==3){
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.MONTH,shortMonths);
 }else {
-if(tokenLen==2){
+if(tokenLen==2||tokenLen>9){
 rule=TwoDigitMonthField.INSTANCE;
 }else {
 rule=UnpaddedMonthField.INSTANCE;
 }
 }
 }
 break;
 case 'd' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'h' :
 
 rule=new TwelveHourField(selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR,tokenLen));
 break;
 case 'H' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR_OF_DAY,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'm' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.MINUTE,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 's' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.SECOND,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'S' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.MILLISECOND,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'E' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.DAY_OF_WEEK,tokenLen<4?shortWeekdays:weekdays);
 break;
 case 'D' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_YEAR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'F' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_WEEK_IN_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'w' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.WEEK_OF_YEAR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'W' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.WEEK_OF_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'a' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.AM_PM,AmPmStrings);
 break;
 case 'k' :
 
 rule=new TwentyFourHourField(selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR_OF_DAY,tokenLen));
 break;
 case 'K' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'z' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=new TimeZoneNameRule(mTimeZone,mTimeZoneForced,mLocale,TimeZone.LONG);
 }else {
 rule=new TimeZoneNameRule(mTimeZone,mTimeZoneForced,mLocale,TimeZone.SHORT);
 }
 break;
 case 'Z' :
 
 if(tokenLen==1){
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_NO_COLON;
 }else {
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_COLON;
 }
 break;
 case '\'' :
 
 String sub=token.substring(1);
 if(sub.length()==1){
 rule=new CharacterLiteral(sub.charAt(0));
 }else {
 rule=new StringLiteral(sub);
 }
 break;
 default :
 
 throw new IllegalArgumentException("Illegal pattern component: "+token);
 }
 rules.add(rule);
 }
 return rules;
 }

 }
 break;

 }else {
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_COLON;

 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_WEEK_IN_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'w' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.WEEK_OF_YEAR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'W' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.WEEK_OF_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'a' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.AM_PM,AmPmStrings);
 break;
 case 'k' :
 
 rule=new TwentyFourHourField(selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR_OF_DAY,tokenLen));
 break;
 case 'K' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'z' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=new TimeZoneNameRule(mTimeZone,mTimeZoneForced,mLocale,TimeZone.LONG);
 }else {
 rule=new TimeZoneNameRule(mTimeZone,mTimeZoneForced,mLocale,TimeZone.SHORT);
 }
 break;
 case 'Z' :
 
 if(tokenLen==1){
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_NO_COLON;
 }else {
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_COLON;
 }
 break;
 case '\'' :
 
 String sub=token.substring(1);
 if(sub.length()==1){
 rule=new CharacterLiteral(sub.charAt(0));
 }else {
 rule=new StringLiteral(sub);
 }
 break;
 default :
 
 throw new IllegalArgumentException("Illegal pattern component: "+token);
 }
 rules.add(rule);
 }
 return rules;
 }

 break;
 case 'm' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.MINUTE,tokenLen);
 break;

 break;
 case 'S' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.MILLISECOND,tokenLen);
 break;

 break;

 break;

 break;

 break;

 break;

 break;

 break;
 case 'K' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'z' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=new TimeZoneNameRule(mTimeZone,mTimeZoneForced,mLocale,TimeZone.LONG);
 }else {
 rule=new TimeZoneNameRule(mTimeZone,mTimeZoneForced,mLocale,TimeZone.SHORT);
 }
 break;
 case 'Z' :
 
 if(tokenLen==1){
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_NO_COLON;
 }else {
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_COLON;
 }
 break;
 case '\'' :

 if(sub.length()==1){
 rule=new CharacterLiteral(sub.charAt(0));
 }else {
 rule=new StringLiteral(sub);
 }
 break;
 default :
 
 throw new IllegalArgumentException("Illegal pattern component: "+token);
 }
 rules.add(rule);
 }
 return rules;
 }

 break;

 }else {

 }else {

 }

 break;

 break;
 case 'H' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR_OF_DAY,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'm' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.MINUTE,tokenLen);
 break;

 break;
 case 'S' :

 break;

 break;

 break;

 break;

 break;

 }else {
 rule=new StringLiteral(sub);
 }
 break;
 default :
 
 throw new IllegalArgumentException("Illegal pattern component: "+token);
 }

 }
 return rules;

 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.MILLISECOND,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'E' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.DAY_OF_WEEK,tokenLen<4?shortWeekdays:weekdays);
 break;
 case 'D' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_YEAR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'F' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_WEEK_IN_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'w' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.WEEK_OF_YEAR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'W' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.WEEK_OF_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'a' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.AM_PM,AmPmStrings);
 break;
 case 'k' :
 
 rule=new TwentyFourHourField(selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR_OF_DAY,tokenLen));
 break;
 case 'K' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'z' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=new TimeZoneNameRule(mTimeZone,mTimeZoneForced,mLocale,TimeZone.LONG);
 }else {
 rule=new TimeZoneNameRule(mTimeZone,mTimeZoneForced,mLocale,TimeZone.SHORT);
 }
 break;
 case 'Z' :
 
 if(tokenLen==1){
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_NO_COLON;
 }else {
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_COLON;
 }
 break;
 case '\'' :
 
 String sub=token.substring(1);
 if(sub.length()==1){
 rule=new CharacterLiteral(sub.charAt(0));
 }else {
 rule=new StringLiteral(sub);
 }
 break;
 default :
 
 throw new IllegalArgumentException("Illegal pattern component: "+token);
 }
 rules.add(rule);
 }
 return rules;
 }

 rule=TwoDigitYearField.INSTANCE;

 }else {
 rule=UnpaddedMonthField.INSTANCE;
 }
 }
 }

 break;

 break;
 case 'H' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR_OF_DAY,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'm' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.MINUTE,tokenLen);
 break;

 break;
 case 'S' :

 break;

 rule=new TextField(Calendar.DAY_OF_WEEK,tokenLen<4?shortWeekdays:weekdays);
 break;
 case 'D' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_YEAR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'F' :

 break;

 break;

 break;
 case 'K' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR,tokenLen);
 break;

 }
 break;
 case 'Z' :

 }else {
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_COLON;
 }
 break;

 rule=new CharacterLiteral(sub.charAt(0));
 }else {
 rule=new StringLiteral(sub);
 }
 break;
 default :

 break;

+assert (shortMonths!=null):"Appointments day is not allowed to be null!";
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.MONTH,shortMonths);
 }else {
 if(tokenLen==2){
 rule=TwoDigitMonthField.INSTANCE;
 }else {
 rule=UnpaddedMonthField.INSTANCE;
 }
 }
 }
 break;

 break;
 case 'h' :
 
 rule=new TwelveHourField(selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR,tokenLen));
 break;
 case 'H' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR_OF_DAY,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'm' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.MINUTE,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 's' :

 break;
 case 'S' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.MILLISECOND,tokenLen);
 break;

 rule=new TextField(Calendar.DAY_OF_WEEK,tokenLen<4?shortWeekdays:weekdays);
 break;

 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_YEAR,tokenLen);
 break;

 break;

 break;

 break;

 break;

 }else {

 }
 break;

 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_NO_COLON;
 }else {
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_COLON;
 }
 break;

 }else {
 rule=new StringLiteral(sub);
 }
 break;
 default :
 
 throw new IllegalArgumentException("Illegal pattern component: "+token);
 }
 rules.add(rule);
 }

 DateFormatSymbols symbols=new DateFormatSymbols(mLocale);
 List<Rule> rules=new ArrayList<Rule>();
 String[] ERAs=symbols.getEras();
 String[] months=symbols.getMonths();
 String[] shortMonths=symbols.getShortMonths();
 String[] weekdays=symbols.getWeekdays();
 String[] shortWeekdays=symbols.getShortWeekdays();
 String[] AmPmStrings=symbols.getAmPmStrings();
 int length=mPattern.length();
 int[] indexRef=new int[1];
 for(int i=0;i<length;i++){
 indexRef[0]=i;
 String token=parseToken(mPattern,indexRef);
 i=indexRef[0];
 int tokenLen=token.length();
 if(tokenLen==0){
 break;
 }
 Rule rule;
 char c=token.charAt(0);
 switch (c){
 case 'G' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.ERA,ERAs);
 break;
 case 'y' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.YEAR,tokenLen);
 }else {
 rule=TwoDigitYearField.INSTANCE;
 }
 break;
 case 'M' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.MONTH,months);
 }else {
 if(tokenLen==3){
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.MONTH,shortMonths);
 }else {
 if(tokenLen==2){
 rule=TwoDigitMonthField.INSTANCE;
 }else {
 rule=UnpaddedMonthField.INSTANCE;
 }
 }
 }
 break;
 case 'd' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'h' :
 
 rule=new TwelveHourField(selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR,tokenLen));
 break;
 case 'H' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR_OF_DAY,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'm' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.MINUTE,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 's' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.SECOND,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'S' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.MILLISECOND,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'E' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.DAY_OF_WEEK,tokenLen<4?shortWeekdays:weekdays);
 break;
 case 'D' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_YEAR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'F' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_WEEK_IN_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'w' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.WEEK_OF_YEAR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'W' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.WEEK_OF_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'a' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.AM_PM,AmPmStrings);
 break;
 case 'k' :
 
 rule=new TwentyFourHourField(selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR_OF_DAY,tokenLen));
 break;
 case 'K' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'z' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=new TimeZoneNameRule(mTimeZone,mTimeZoneForced,mLocale,TimeZone.LONG);
 }else {
 rule=new TimeZoneNameRule(mTimeZone,mTimeZoneForced,mLocale,TimeZone.SHORT);
 }
 break;
 case 'Z' :
 
 if(tokenLen==1){
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_NO_COLON;
 }else {
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_COLON;
 }
 break;
 case '\'' :
 
 String sub=token.substring(1);
 if(sub.length()==1){
 rule=new CharacterLiteral(sub.charAt(0));
+rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.MILLISECOND,tokenLen);
 }else {
 rule=new StringLiteral(sub);
 }
 break;
 default :
 
 throw new IllegalArgumentException("Illegal pattern component: "+token);
 }
 rules.add(rule);
 }
 return rules;
 }

 DateFormatSymbols symbols=new DateFormatSymbols(mLocale);
 List<Rule> rules=new ArrayList<Rule>();

 String[] shortMonths=symbols.getShortMonths();
 String[] weekdays=symbols.getWeekdays();

 String[] AmPmStrings=symbols.getAmPmStrings();
 int length=mPattern.length();
 int[] indexRef=new int[1];
 for(int i=0;i<length;i++){
 indexRef[0]=i;
 String token=parseToken(mPattern,indexRef);
 i=indexRef[0];
 int tokenLen=token.length();
 if(tokenLen==0){
 break;
 }
 Rule rule;
 char c=token.charAt(0);
 switch (c){
 case 'G' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.ERA,ERAs);
 break;
 case 'y' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.YEAR,tokenLen);
 }else {
 rule=TwoDigitYearField.INSTANCE;
 }
 break;
 case 'M' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.MONTH,months);
 }else {
 if(tokenLen==3){
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.MONTH,shortMonths);
 }else {
 if(tokenLen==2){
 rule=TwoDigitMonthField.INSTANCE;
 }else {
 rule=UnpaddedMonthField.INSTANCE;
+rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.MILLISECOND,tokenLen);
 }
 }
 }
 break;
 case 'd' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'h' :
 
 rule=new TwelveHourField(selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR,tokenLen));
 break;
 case 'H' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR_OF_DAY,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'm' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.MINUTE,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 's' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.SECOND,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'S' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.MILLISECOND,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'E' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.DAY_OF_WEEK,tokenLen<4?shortWeekdays:weekdays);
 break;
 case 'D' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_YEAR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'F' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.DAY_OF_WEEK_IN_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'w' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.WEEK_OF_YEAR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'W' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.WEEK_OF_MONTH,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'a' :
 
 rule=new TextField(Calendar.AM_PM,AmPmStrings);
 break;
 case 'k' :
 
 rule=new TwentyFourHourField(selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR_OF_DAY,tokenLen));
 break;
 case 'K' :
 
 rule=selectNumberRule(Calendar.HOUR,tokenLen);
 break;
 case 'z' :
 
 if(tokenLen>=4){
 rule=new TimeZoneNameRule(mTimeZone,mTimeZoneForced,mLocale,TimeZone.LONG);
 }else {
 rule=new TimeZoneNameRule(mTimeZone,mTimeZoneForced,mLocale,TimeZone.SHORT);
 }
 break;
 case 'Z' :
 
 if(tokenLen==1){
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_NO_COLON;
 }else {
 rule=TimeZoneNumberRule.INSTANCE_COLON;
 }
 break;
 case '\'' :
 
 String sub=token.substring(1);
 if(sub.length()==1){
 rule=new CharacterLiteral(sub.charAt(0));
 }else {
 rule=new StringLiteral(sub);
 }
 break;
 default :
 
 throw new IllegalArgumentException("Illegal pattern component: "+token);
 }
 rules.add(rule);
 }
 return rules;
 }

 if(tokenLen==2){
 rule=TwoDigitMonthField.INSTANCE;
 }else {
 rule=UnpaddedMonthField.INSTANCE;
 }

 break;

 indexRef[0]=i;

 i=indexRef[0];
 int tokenLen=token.length();
 if(tokenLen==0){
 break;
 }
